Description_lang: Interrupting a spell with Skull Bash reduces the remaining cooldown of Tiger's Fury, Survival Instincts, and $?s252216[Tiger Dash][Dash] by $s1 sec.

description_blz.en_US: Interrupting a spell with Skull Bash reduces the remaining cooldown of Tiger's Fury, Survival Instincts, and Dash by 10 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Interrumpir un hechizo con Testarazo reduce 10 s el tiempo de reutilización restante de Furia del tigre, Instintos de supervivencia y Carrerilla.
description_blz.pt_BR: Ao interromper um feitiço com Esmagar Crânio, a recarga restante de Fúria do Tigre, Instintos de Sobrevivência e Arremetida é reduzida em 10 s.
description_blz.de_DE: Wenn Ihr einen Zauber mit 'Schädelstoß' unterbrecht, wird die verbleibende Abklingzeit von 'Tigerfuror', 'Überlebensinstinkte' und 'Spurt' um 10 Sek. verringert.
description_blz.en_GB: Interrupting a spell with Skull Bash reduces the remaining cooldown of Tiger's Fury, Survival Instincts, and Dash by 10 sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Interrumpir un hechizo con Testarazo reduce 10 s el tiempo de reutilización restante de Furia del tigre, Instintos de supervivencia y Carrerilla.
description_blz.fr_FR: Interrompre un sort avec Coup de crâne réduit de 10 s le temps de recharge de Fureur du tigre, Instincts de survie et Célérité.
description_blz.it_IT: Interrompere un lancio d'incantesimi con Craniata riduce il tempo di recupero restante di Furia della Tigre, Istinto di Sopravvivenza e Slancio di 10 s.
description_blz.ru_RU: Когда вы прерываете заклинания "Лобовой атакой", время восстановления "Тигриного неистовства", "Инстинктов выживания" и "Порыва" сокращается на 10 сек.
description_blz.ko_KR: 두개골 강타로 주문 시전을 방해하면 호랑이의 분노, 생존 본능, 질주의 남은 재사용 대기시간이 10초만큼 감소합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 以碎顱猛擊中斷施法可使猛虎之怒、求生本能和突進的剩餘冷卻時間縮短10秒。
description_blz.zh_CN: 用迎头痛击打断敌人施法可使猛虎之怒、生存本能和急奔的剩余冷却时间减少10秒。
